CRM


Internal dashboard


Without logging in again.

💎 Now Let’s Make It Real (Rails Implementation)
Gem used:
gem 'omniauth-saml'

Initializer:
Rails.application.config.middleware.use OmniAuth::Builder do
  provider :saml,
    assertion_consumer_service_url: "https://yourapp.com/auth/saml/callback",
    issuer: "https://yourapp.com",
    idp_sso_target_url: "https://adfs.company.com/adfs/ls/",
    idp_cert: ENV['ADFS_CERT'],
    name_identifier_format: "urn:oasis:names:tc:SAML:1.1:nameid-format:emailAddress"
end

Callback controller:
def create
  auth = request.env["omniauth.auth"]

  user = User.find_or_create_by(email: auth.info.email)
  sign_in(user)
end


